{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"5f03dd75-fad1-4be7-b69d-a2db50a85843","content":"Exit code 8 in Microsoft.Testing.Platform means **\"no tests discovered\"** — this is the intended behavioral change from VSTest, which returned 0 in that scenario. Since your tests are conditionally compiled out (via `#if INCLUDE_SLOW_TESTS`), the runner finds zero tests and exits with 8.\n\nThe fix is a single property in your `.csproj`:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_013HPinjcd4UzmfX83x8TnNE","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Fixing zero-tests exit code"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01NUuupZKiv9aCT6J9M8hW6V","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-7408ea2e6013455288be7b1c30b3760c/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n    <TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>0</TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-7408ea2e6013455288be7b1c30b3760c/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"8f280dd6-8902-40fa-a853-04dfdf3259cd","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The issue is clear. With Microsoft.Testing.Platform (enabled by `EnableMSTestRunner`), exit code 8 means \"no tests were found.\" When `INCLUDE_SLOW_TESTS` is not defined, the entire test class is compiled out, leaving zero tests, and the test runner returns exit code 8.\n\nThe fix is to set the MSBuild property `<TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>0</TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>` in the project file. This tells Microsoft.Testing.Platform to return exit code 0 when no tests are discovered instead of 8.\n\n\nI should verify this works by running `dotnet test` to confirm the exit code behavior changes as expected.","outputTokens":542,"requestId":"703A:1CDC41:E06E473:F6A5698:69F2A8C6"},"id":"d0076062-2aeb-4927-b239-90444000016d","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:56:48.083Z","parentId":"a7495619-7a0d-4fcf-bbb5-beed945822e0"}
